node.text: Giving you look at my little history with my guitar. A relationship I am revisiting. I show you my guitars, have a FaceTime with my Dad to ask about when I was a kid and give you a run through of where I’m at. This is getting to know me, the long answer. Something personal I thought I would share.

node.text:
I've had pets my whole life and for the first time I'm without a little companion…

It's been tough on me but I need to be patient and wait a while before I can take on another fur baby. Life has been very hectic so I need the time to focus and give myself…

Missing my Lu 💔👼
